- **Navigation**: Navigate to any page using voice (e.g., "go to dashboard", "open notes")### üé§ Voice Commands## FeaturesThe Voice Navigator is a comprehensive accessibility feature designed to help users with dyslexia and other visual or motor impairments navigate the website using voice commands.## Overview:root {
  --background: #050505;
  --foreground: #ededed;
  --color-background: var(--background);
  --color-foreground: var(--foreground);
  --font-sans: var(--font-geist-sans);
  --font-mono: var(--font-geist-mono);
}

body {
  background: var(--background);
  color: var(--foreground);
  font-family: var(--font-sans), Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Custom Scroll Animations */
.scroll-anim {
  transition:
    opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1),
    transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
  will-change: opacity, transform;
}

.scroll-anim.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translate(0, 0);
}

/* 3D Utilities */
.perspective-1000 {
  perspective: 1000px;
}

.transform-style-3d {
  transform-style: preserve-3d;
}

.backface-hidden {
  backface-visibility: hidden;
}

/* Custom Scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 8px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: #050505;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: #333;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: #555;
}

/* High Contrast Mode */
body.high-contrast {
  --background: #000000;
  --foreground: #ffffff;
  background: #000000 !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
}

body.high-contrast a {
  color: #ffff00 !important;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

body.high-contrast button {
  border: 2px solid #ffffff !important;
}

body.high-contrast input,
body.high-contrast textarea,
body.high-contrast select {
  background: #000000 !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
  border: 2px solid #ffffff !important;
}

/* Accessibility Focus Styles */
*:focus-visible {
  outline: 3px solid #4a90e2;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Dyslexia-Friendly Styles */
body.dyslexia-mode {
  line-height: 1.8;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  word-spacing: 0.16em;
}

body.dyslexia-mode p {
  margin-bottom: 1.5em;
}

body.dyslexia-mode h1,
body.dyslexia-mode h2,
body.dyslexia-mode h3,
body.dyslexia-mode h4,
body.dyslexia-mode h5,
body.dyslexia-mode h6 {
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.75em;
}
